27#ifndef HB_SUBSET_HH
28#define HB_SUBSET_HH
29
30
31#include "hb.hh"
32
33#include "hb-subset.h"
34
35#include "hb-machinery.hh"
36#include "hb-serialize.hh"
37#include "hb-subset-input.hh"
38#include "hb-subset-plan.hh"
39
40struct hb_subset_context_t :
41 hb_dispatch_context_t<hb_subset_context_t, bool, HB_DEBUG_SUBSET>
42{
43 const char *get_name () { return "SUBSET"; }
44 static return_t default_return_value () { return true; }
45
46 private:
47 template <typename T, typename ...Ts> auto
48 _dispatch (const T &obj, hb_priority<1>, Ts&&... ds) HB_AUTO_RETURN
49 ( obj.subset (this, std::forward<Ts> (ds)...) )
50 template <typename T, typename ...Ts> auto
51 _dispatch (const T &obj, hb_priority<0>, Ts&&... ds) HB_AUTO_RETURN
52 ( obj.dispatch (this, std::forward<Ts> (ds)...) )
53 public:
54 template <typename T, typename ...Ts> auto
55 dispatch (const T &obj, Ts&&... ds) HB_AUTO_RETURN
56 ( _dispatch (obj, hb_prioritize, std::forward<Ts> (ds)...) )
57
58 hb_blob_t *source_blob;
59 hb_subset_plan_t *plan;
60 hb_serialize_context_t *serializer;
61 hb_tag_t table_tag;
62
63 hb_subset_context_t (hb_blob_t *source_blob_,
64 hb_subset_plan_t *plan_,
65 hb_serialize_context_t *serializer_,
66 hb_tag_t table_tag_) :
67 source_blob (source_blob_),
68 plan (plan_),
69 serializer (serializer_),
70 table_tag (table_tag_) {}
71};
72
73
74#endif /* HB_SUBSET_HH */
